==English==

===Etymology===

From ''meso-'' (medium, intermediate) + ''-fauna'' (animals).

===Noun===

'''mesofauna''' (''plural'' '''mesofaunae''' or '''mesofaunas''')

# A general term for a group including any [[animal]] of [[intermediate]] size, typically [[invertebrate]]s, such as [[bivalve]]s, [[arthropod]]s, [[insect]]s, and [[annelid]]s.

